56050_4ba0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180807%2Flarge%2F1533656050_4ba0.jpg&h=7b0ab4e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其間背心男一度佔上風，惟白衫長褲男手持貌似電筒的硬物，打得他頭破血流，拖鞋都飛脫。整個打交情況持續約10分鐘，吸引大批街坊圍觀，其間有人大叫：「大家都係人，唔好打親呀」未幾便有一名熱心男街坊上前勸阻，惟白衫長褲男傷人後欲偕女方離開現場，但背心男阻止，再度拉扯糾纏，並跌倒地上扭作一團，白衫長褲男手持的電筒亦飛脫跌在地上。其後兩人分別爬起身，背心男一度走入附近便利店，手持玻璃樽折返現場，惟對方男女已離開。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後接報到場調查，惟白衫長褲男及女伴已經逃之夭夭，背心男頭部受傷送院治理。據悉，雙方早前在網上一貓狗討論區疑意見不合，於是相約在晚上到小西灣邨巴士總站對出見面，未料3人現身後，其間兩名男事主一言不合先是口角，繼而大打出手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180808/58536114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F58536114&d=3HuLyxwtD1g7xltfCt1I5P755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e6781878\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F58536114&h=a67aa966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180808/58536114</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"比武姐,打咩柒野交"},{"pid":"5f18c6491b82892e7d070a3609dd85aa5a1df184","tid":771314,"uid":152788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:44:20.000Z","msg":"條女做咩？"},{"pid":"43d68a67830c18a859601b39330723f2ebfc68f4","tid":771314,"uid":7375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T04:07:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eca7c1e945374d657c6d37562057fbabb9ee7884","tid":771314,"uid":129374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"灰色衫果個係裁判! <br />\n好明顯背心男點數分輸咗"},{"pid":"5dff15c481929c2c090e35171553a3ad1f66dddb","tid":771314,"uid":190116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"d5b7f7f